String.string: You tuwangis know anything about the Red Raiders?
Raiders? We have important training to do! Don't bother us!
Please, this is important. Lives are at stake.
Ha! Training is important too! But if you soft skins can't handle it...
Soft? You're talking to one of the federation's greatest heroes!
Oooh, a hero! Maybe you can survive our training, then? Show us why we should care about Raiders?
This doesn't seem too hard. Let's do it. For the federation!
